            <div class="time-estimate">‚è± 6 MINUTES</div>
            
            <div class="lesson-chunk">
                Multiply numerators together for the result numerator. Multiply denominators together for the result denominator. Reduce fractions to the lowest common term. 
            </div>
            
            <div class="critical-principle">
                (A/B) * (C/D) = (A*C) / (B*D)
            </div>
            
            <div class="example-box">
                <strong>TACTICAL EXAMPLE:</strong> 1/2 supply route is secured. 1/3 of secured route needs repair. Total route needing repair: 1/2 * 1/3 = 1/6.
            </div>
            
