            <div class="time-estimate">‚è± 6 MINUTES</div>
            
            <div class="lesson-chunk">
                Division requires flipping the second fraction (reciprocal). Change the operation from division to multiplication. Execute multiplication protocol as defined above.
            </div>
            
            <div class="critical-principle">
                (A/B) / (C/D) = (A/B) * (D/C)
            </div>
            
